messages.message: I noticed on `master`, my prettier precommit hook is adding double quotes instead of single quotes. @mfichman The prettier version was bumped from v2.7.0 to v4.0.0-alpha.8 in this PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/70378/files) yesterday. Is this an intentional bump?
Yeah, I bumped it cause I kept getting a warning. We can revert if it’s causing problems.
I’m just going to revert just the prettier change. The warning shouldn’t reappear again.
